		{
			dependencies: ["3BAA2A254E052AC1"]
			description: [
				"Now pop a &6princess and drone into an apiary,&r and watch the magic happen! Bees can generate some &6very useful resources&r in their combs; initially, though, you'll have to process said combs on &6a cutting board.&r"
				""
				"At first, you'll only get beeswax and honey drops, alongside some dead logs..."
				""
				"&7Tip: wasteland bees need dead bushes as their 'flowers'!"
