		{
			dependencies: ["6C972BEC949FEF25"]
			description: [
				"At some point, you'll want to take a closer look at your bees - the &6Analyzer&r allows you to examine what genes exactly any given bee has, for the low cost of a single honey drop."
				""
				"The &6Apid Library&r shows you what mutations you can create with a bee's species."
				""
				"The &6Microscope&r allows you to research bee species, giving you a higher chance to mutate bees into a researched species."
				""
				"&7Tip: the Microscope is a great way to get rid of unnecessary drones you have! Read the Apiarist Field Guide for more info on it."
			]
			icon: "complicated_bees:analyzer"
