				""
				"Their rocky combs produce much more wax and honey than their wasteland cousins, but more importantly, they can rarely produce &6Copper Combs&r as a specialty."
				""
				"&7Tip: specialties are only produced when a bee is ecstatic! To make a bee ecstatic, you have to have its housing climate &lexactly&r&7 match the bee's preferred climate. Either breed it so that it prefers the hot dry wastes, or use special frames to adjust the temperature and humidity!"
