		{
			dependencies: [
				"5AFED2AAA3E9F13D"
				"710F5DFED74D5098"
			]
			description: [
				"The &6Mellarium&r is a multiblock version of the apiary, with the ability to add modules that can help you in a variety of ways."
				""
				"The most concrete thing a Mellarium can do is give you more than three frame slots, using &6Frame Housings.&r This means you can get, in the best case, &l&oSTACKS&r of combs every bee tick."
