				"You'll want to prioritize inserting any apiary outputs into the apiary first, since it &6only accepts bees.&r To do this, you'll have to either take advantage of the way &6Embers pipes try to go straight before turning,&r or use a buffer chest for Mekanism since those pipes &4don't insert items into blocks they extract from.&r Remaining items will move on to be inserted into an output chest."
				""
				"As a side note, frames cannot be auto-inserted into apiaries - but they &6might be automatable into a larger form of bee housing...&r"
				""
				"Example setups for either of those mods can be found as pictures near this quest once you complete it."
			]
